snippet.title: Asterix & Obelix XXL 3: The Crystal Menhir | Launch Trailer | PS4
snippet.description: Set off on an exciting adventure and immerse yourself in the world of Asterix! Alone or in co-op, explore the lands of the Roman empire and unravel the mystery of the Crystal Menhir and its incredible powers!
